ARTISTIC REASON set the pace from off the rail facing pressure by an outside foe up the backstretch, drifted out leaving the far turn then further in upper stretch, was soon overtaken and weakened thereafter. PURPLE SHIRT got away slowly, settled at the back off the inside, swung nine wide into upper stretch, ran on with mild late interest. KINETIC SWAGGER raced outside four to five wide early, failed to rally. MELINA'S DREAM tucked in behind the leading pair heading to the first turn saving ground along the rail through the first turn, dropped back on the far turn, tired.
